text: Kanbekovo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Bogdanovsky Selsoviet, Miyakinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 483 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 19 km from Kirgiz-Miyaki, 4 km from Bogdanovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Miyakinsky District
title: Kanbekovo
